      <title>華倫·巴菲特表示波克夏虧本出售了全部派拉蒙股份</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/warren-buffett-says-berkshire-sold-entire-paramount-holdings-loss-2024-05-04/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[華倫巴菲特週六表示，波克夏海瑟威公司虧本出售了在媒體和娛樂公司派拉蒙全球的全部股份，他對這項決定承擔全部責任。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/warren-buffett-says-berkshire-sold-entire-paramount-holdings-loss-2024-05-04/</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 04 May 2024 19:59:33 GMT</pubDate>
