      <title>伯克希爾高層表示針對其公用事業業務的野火索賠毫無根據</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/berkshire-exec-calls-wildfire-claims-against-utility-unfounded-2024-05-04/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一位高層週六表示，沃倫·巴菲特領導的伯克希爾·哈撒韋公司將應對因山火而針對其公用事業業務提起的所有訴訟，因為這些案件「毫無根據」。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/berkshire-exec-calls-wildfire-claims-against-utility-unfounded-2024-05-04/</guid>
